{"id":7668,"date":"2020-01-08T08:28:07","date_gmt":"2020-01-08T08:28:07","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/?p=7668"},"modified":"2021-02-27T03:37:19","modified_gmt":"2021-02-27T03:37:19","slug":"meo-cho-tranh-nghe-thuat-trang-tri-noi-that-hien-dai","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/meo-cho-tranh-nghe-thuat-trang-tri-noi-that-hien-dai\/","title":{"rendered":"M\u1eb9o Ch\u1ecdn Tranh Ngh\u1ec7 Thu\u1eadt Trang Tr\u00ed N\u1ed9i Th\u1ea5t Hi\u1ec7n \u0110\u1ea1i Cho Kh\u00f4ng Gian S\u1ed1ng \u1ea4n T\u01b0\u1ee3ng"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>M\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1eb7p nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0: \u201cL\u00e0m th\u1ebf n\u00e0o t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00fang b\u1ee9c tranh ngh\u1ec7 thu\u1eadt cho ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh?\u201d. T\u00e1c ph\u1ea9m ngh\u1ec7 thu\u1eadt hay b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 v\u1eadt d\u1ee5ng decor l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec gi\u00fap x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u00ednh c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng. Vi\u1ec7c trang tr\u00ed n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 khi c\u00e1c m\u1ea3ng n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eafn k\u1ebft v\u1edbi nhau, t\u1ea1o n\u00ean kh\u00f4ng gian h\u00e0i h\u00f2a, s\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ed9ng cho ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y <a href=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/\">Byzan<\/a> xin chia s\u1ebb m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00fang b\u1ee9c <strong><a href=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/tin-tuc\/\">tranh ngh\u1ec7 thu\u1eadt trang tr\u00ed n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t<\/a><\/strong> cho m\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/tranh-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-7669\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/tranh-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/tranh-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/tranh-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/tranh.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/Byzannoithathiendai\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Tranh trang tr\u00ed cho ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch<\/a><\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Kh\u00f4ng gian ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng th\u00fa v\u1ecb nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 trang tr\u00ed ngh\u1ec7 thu\u1eadt, th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n gu th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 t\u00ednh c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a gia ch\u1ee7 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch. C\u0169ng ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt gia ch\u1ee7 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y \u00e1p l\u1ef1c khi ch\u1ecdn <strong>tranh trang tr\u00ed<\/strong> cho khu v\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi ch\u01a1i nh\u00e0. Ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00fang <strong>b\u1ee9c tranh ngh\u1ec7 thu\u1eadt trang tr\u00ed n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t<\/strong> l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 k\u00edch th\u00edch cu\u1ed9c tr\u00f2 chuy\u1ec7n, t\u1ea1o c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i, t\u1ef1 tin giao ti\u1ebfp trong kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng. B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn m\u1ed9t b\u1ee9c tranh canvas hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1edbn ho\u1eb7c b\u1ed9 tranh ngh\u1ec7 thu\u1eadt t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/ph%C3%B2ng-kh%C3%A1ch-2-1024x695.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-7670\"\/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/ph%C3%B2ng-kh%C3%A1ch-1-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-7671\"\/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Tuy nhi\u00ean, ngh\u1ec7 thu\u1eadt trang tr\u00ed n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u1ee9c tranh in ho\u1eb7c v\u1ea3i, \u0111\u00f4i khi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c. B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 suy ngh\u0129 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn b\u1ea3n sao k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1edbn qu\u1ed1c k\u1ef3 ho\u1eb7c s\u1eebng Stag, h\u00e3y t\u1ea1m qu\u00ean nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2D v\u00e0 b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd t\u00ecm th\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t t\u00e1c ph\u1ea9m \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n r\u00f5 t\u00ednh c\u00e1ch v\u1ec1 m\u00ecnh.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/ph%C3%B2ng-kh%C3%A1ch-4.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-7672\"\/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Tranh trang tr\u00ed n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t ph\u00f2ng b\u1ebfp&nbsp;<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>M\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng th\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1ecb gia ch\u1ee7 l\u00e3ng qu\u00ean v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t ngh\u1ec7 thu\u1eadt ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng b\u1ebfp. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi &#8211; \u201cNgh\u1ec7 thu\u1eadt c\u00f3 c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y?\u201d.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/ph%C3%B2ng-b%E1%BA%BFp-1-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-7675\"\/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped aligncenter wp-block-gallery-1 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/ph%C3%B2ng-b%E1%BA%BFp-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"7674\" class=\"wp-image-7674\"\/><\/figure><\/li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/ph%C3%B2ng-b%E1%BA%BFp-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"7676\" class=\"wp-image-7676\"\/><\/figure><\/li><\/ul><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Nh\u00e0 b\u1ebfp th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 \u201ctr\u00e1i tim c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0\u201d, n\u01a1i t\u00ecnh y\u00eau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eedi g\u1eafm qua nh\u1eefng m\u00f3n \u0103n \u1ea5m n\u00f3ng, th\u01a1m n\u1ed3ng. L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn m\u1ed9t b\u1ee9c tranh canvas th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 h\u00e0i h\u01b0\u1edbc ho\u1eb7c m\u00e0u s\u1eafc t\u01b0\u01a1i m\u00e1t s\u1ebd gi\u00fap ch\u00fang ta m\u1ec9m c\u01b0\u1eddi, v\u00e0 kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian n\u1ea5u n\u01b0\u1edbng tr\u1edf n\u00ean th\u01b0 gi\u00e3n h\u01a1n! V\u1ecb tr\u00ed ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p trong ph\u00f2ng b\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n ngh\u1ec7 thu\u1eadt c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 treo g\u1ea7n b\u00e0n \u0103n ho\u1eb7c kh\u00f4ng gian ph\u00eda tr\u00ean t\u1ee7 l\u1eedng.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Tranh ngh\u1ec7 thu\u1eadt cho ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7&nbsp;<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 l\u00e0 n\u01a1i ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i, n\u01a1i th\u01b0 gi\u00e3n v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng b\u1ee9c <strong>tranh ngh\u1ec7 thu\u1eadt trang tr\u00ed n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t<\/strong> n\u00ean th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Nh\u1eefng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 treo c\u00e1c t\u00e1c ph\u1ea9m ngh\u1ec7 thu\u1eadt trong ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7, l\u00e0 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp ph\u00eda tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u01b0\u1eddng ho\u1eb7c tr\u00ean b\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n gi\u01b0\u1eddng ng\u1ee7. K\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc tranh l\u1edbn l\u00e0 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 n\u00ean l\u01b0u \u00fd treo ngang t\u1ea7m m\u1eaft, kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean treo qu\u00e1 cao s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn m\u1eaft b\u1ecb m\u1ecfi.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/ph%C3%B2ng-ng%E1%BB%A7-1-1024x717.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-7677\"\/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\u00e1c b\u1ee9c tranh tr\u1eebu t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f3 m\u00e0u s\u1eafc nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng chi ti\u1ebft t\u1ed1i gi\u1ea3n nh\u01b0 c\u00e2y c\u1ecf, chim mu\u00f4ng,&#8230;t\u1ea1o c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c th\u01b0 th\u00e1i, thanh t\u1ecbnh gi\u00fap gi\u1ea5c ng\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n s\u00e2u h\u01a1n. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng gia ch\u1ee7 c\u00f3 c\u00e1 t\u00ednh, kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean b\u1ecf qua nh\u1eefng b\u1ee9c tranh trang tr\u00ed v\u1edbi hai t\u00f4ng m\u00e0u kinh \u0111i\u1ec3n tr\u1eafng, \u0111en kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd l\u1ed7i m\u1ed1t, c\u00f2n t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 cho ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 tr\u1edf n\u00ean \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/ph%C3%B2ng-ng%E1%BB%A7-2-1024x896.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-7678\"\/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Trang trang tr\u00ed ph\u00f2ng t\u1eafm<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Ph\u00f2ng t\u1eafm l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng gian kh\u00e1c th\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1ecb gia ch\u1ee7 b\u1ecf qu\u00ean v\u1edbi ngh\u1ec7 thu\u1eadt \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. C\u00e1c t\u00e1c ph\u1ea9m ngh\u1ec7 thu\u1eadt b\u1ea1n ch\u1ecdn n\u00ean \u0111i c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a ph\u00f2ng t\u1eafm. V\u00ed d\u1ee5, n\u1ebfu \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u00f2ng ph\u1ee5 b\u1ea1n n\u00ean b\u00e1m v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng b\u1ee9c tranh t\u00f4ng m\u00e0u s\u00e1ng h\u01a1n v\u00e0 vui nh\u1ed9n h\u01a1n. N\u1ebfu \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng t\u1eafm ch\u00ednh, h\u00e3y l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn nh\u1eefng b\u1ee9c tranh \u00eam d\u1ecbu, nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/ph%C3%B2ng-t%E1%BA%AFm-3-1024x802.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-7679\"\/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/ph%C3%B2ng-t%E1%BA%AFm-6.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-7687\"\/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0110\u1ec3 ph\u00f2ng t\u1eafm ngh\u1ec7 thu\u1eadt h\u01a1n, b\u1ea1n n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn nh\u1eefng t\u00e1c ph\u1ea9m tr\u1eebu t\u01b0\u1ee3ng theo b\u1ed9 ho\u1eb7c c\u00f9ng ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7t c\u1ea1nh nhau. Nh\u1eefng ch\u1ed7 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 treo nh\u1eefng b\u1ee9c tranh l\u00e0 tr\u00ean nh\u00e0 v\u1ec7 sinh, tr\u00ean b\u1ed3n t\u1eafm ho\u1eb7c tr\u00ean m\u00f3c kh\u0103n\/ \u00e1o cho\u00e0ng.&nbsp;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>M\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf th\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1eb7p nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0:\u201cL\u00e0m th\u1ebf n\u00e0o t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00fang b\u1ee9c tranh ngh\u1ec7 thu\u1eadt trang tr\u00ed n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t cho ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0?\u201d<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":7669,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[154],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-7668","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-chia-se-kien-thuc"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/7668","targetHints":{"allow"